{"id":11864,"date":"2020-08-31T07:42:29","date_gmt":"2020-08-31T07:42:29","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/?page_id=11864"},"modified":"2021-05-18T10:31:06","modified_gmt":"2021-05-18T10:31:06","slug":"zoom-sur-la-normalisation","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/normalisation\/zoom-sur-la-normalisation\/","title":{"rendered":"Zoom sur la Normalisation"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"limit-wrapper\"><div class=\"row \"><div class=\"wpv-grid grid-1-1  wpv-first-level first unextended has-extended-padding\" style=\"padding-top:0.05px;padding-bottom:0.05px;\" id=\"wpv-column-687cbe84912aab4f53eaa7e4a4d09358\" ><div class=\"row \"><div class=\"wpv-grid grid-1-1  first unextended has-extended-padding\" style=\"padding-top:0.05px;padding-bottom:0.05px;\" id=\"wpv-column-699aaa5292674046c828361058d8776c\" ><div class=\"row \"><div class=\"wpv-grid grid-1-1  first unextended has-extended-padding\" style=\"padding-top:0.05px;padding-bottom:0.05px;\" id=\"wpv-column-bfd4fbd01acac55b8e07c7ed03bf5116\" ><div class=\"row \"><div class=\"wpv-grid grid-1-2  first unextended no-extended-padding\" style=\"padding-top:0.05px;padding-bottom:0.05px;\" id=\"wpv-column-d5b4e7d5ca7a0c40def1aeca6de6ee46\" >\n<div  data-target=\"_self\" class=\"linkarea clearfix accent5  background-transparent\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"last\"><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>QU&rsquo;EST CE QUE LA NORMALISATION ?\u00a0<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">La normalisation est un proc\u00e9d\u00e9 par lequel des accords sont pris entre des parties int\u00e9ress\u00e9es sur des sp\u00e9cifications<\/p>\n<p><strong>Loi n\u00b0 006\/2014 du 28 aout 2014 <\/strong>instituant le syst\u00e8me national de Normalisation : La normalisation consiste \u00e0 \u00e9tablir\u00a0 des <strong>exigences<\/strong>, des <strong>sp\u00e9cifications<\/strong> ou des <strong>r\u00e8gles techniques<\/strong> applicables \u00e0 la fabrication ou \u00e0 la commercialisation des produits, biens ou services.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><div class=\"push \" style=\"height:10px\"><\/div><\/div>\n\t<\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"wpv-grid grid-1-2  unextended no-extended-padding\" style=\"padding-top:0.05px;padding-bottom:0.05px;\" id=\"wpv-column-a420edf569a89754b75a979f672af13b\" >\n<div  data-target=\"_self\" class=\"linkarea clearfix accent5  background-transparent\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"first\"><img width=\"500\" height=\"250\" src=\"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/mission.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/mission.jpg 500w, https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/mission-300x150.jpg 300w, https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/mission-360x180.jpg 360w, https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/mission-262x131.jpg 262w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"last\"><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>MISSION DE LA NORMALISATION<\/strong><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\u00c9laborer et mettre en \u0153uvre\u00a0 la politique et la strat\u00e9gie nationale de normalisation et de la qualit\u00e9 ;<\/li>\n<li>Produire les normes gabonaises \u00e0 travers les comit\u00e9s techniques\u00a0;<\/li>\n<li>Faire de la veille normative sur les normes gabonaises et internationales.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><div class=\"push \" style=\"height:10px\"><\/div><\/div>\n\t<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"row \"><div class=\"wpv-grid grid-1-2  first unextended no-extended-padding\" style=\"padding-top:0.05px;padding-bottom:0.05px;\" id=\"wpv-column-cdefcb79449f94a2891efe3433f934f3\" >\n<div  data-target=\"_self\" class=\"linkarea clearfix accent5  background-transparent\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"first\"><img width=\"500\" height=\"250\" src=\"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/but.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/but.jpg 500w, https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/but-300x150.jpg 300w, https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/but-360x180.jpg 360w, https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/but-262x131.jpg 262w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"last\"><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>OBJECTIF DE LA NORMALISATION<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">De fa\u00e7on g\u00e9n\u00e9rale, l\u2019objectif de la normalisation est de fournir des documents de r\u00e9f\u00e9rence comportant des solutions \u00e0 des probl\u00e8mes techniques et commerciaux concernant les produits, biens et services, qui se posent de fa\u00e7on r\u00e9p\u00e9t\u00e9e dans des relations entre partenaires socio-\u00e9conomiques, scientifiques et techniques.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><div class=\"push \" style=\"height:10px\"><\/div><\/div>\n\t<\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"wpv-grid grid-1-2  unextended no-extended-padding\" style=\"padding-top:0.05px;padding-bottom:0.05px;\" id=\"wpv-column-aa0942c263d2e082d2b3b6617dccd061\" >\n<div  data-target=\"_self\" class=\"linkarea clearfix accent5  background-transparent\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"last\"><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>LES PRINCIPES DE LA NORMALISATION<\/strong><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>La transparence\u00a0:<\/strong> Tous les supports sont accessibles \u00e0 toutes les parties int\u00e9ress\u00e9es\u00a0;<\/li>\n<li><strong>La coh\u00e9rence\u00a0:<\/strong> les normes ne doivent pas \u00eatre contradictoires\u00a0;<\/li>\n<li><strong>Le consensus\u00a0: <\/strong>les d\u00e9cisions sont prises suivant des proc\u00e9dures consensuelles\u00a0;<\/li>\n<li><strong>L\u2019impartialit\u00e9\u00a0: <\/strong>L\u2019\u00e9laboration des normes se fait sans parti pris\u00a0<strong>;<\/strong><\/li>\n<li><strong>L\u2019ouverture\u00a0: <\/strong>les travaux d\u2019\u00e9laboration des normes sont ouverts \u00e0 tous et les int\u00e9r\u00eats de chacun pris en compte\u00a0;<\/li>\n<li><strong>La pertinence\u00a0: <\/strong>les normes sont examin\u00e9es et mises \u00e0 jour \u00e0 intervalles r\u00e9guliers.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><div class=\"push \" style=\"height:10px\"><\/div><\/div>\n\t<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"row \"><div class=\"wpv-grid grid-1-2  first unextended no-extended-padding\" style=\"padding-top:0.05px;padding-bottom:0.05px;\" id=\"wpv-column-ed77684ae2f719502973742084bbae2a\" >\n<div  data-target=\"_self\" class=\"linkarea clearfix accent5  background-transparent\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"first\"><img width=\"500\" height=\"250\" src=\"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/normes.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/normes.jpg 500w, https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/normes-300x150.jpg 300w, https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/normes-360x180.jpg 360w, https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/normes-262x131.jpg 262w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"last\"><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>C\u2019EST QUOI LA NORME ?<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p><strong>Selon le Guide ISO\/ CEI 2<\/strong> la norme est un <strong>document<\/strong> \u00e9tabli par <strong>consensus <\/strong>et approuv\u00e9 par un <strong>organisme reconnu<\/strong> qui fournit pour des usages communs et r\u00e9p\u00e9t\u00e9s, des r\u00e9sultats garantissant <strong>un niveau d\u2019ordre optimal<\/strong> dans un contexte donn\u00e9.<\/p>\n<p>Une norme est un document qui pr\u00e9cise des d\u00e9finitions, exigences, sp\u00e9cifications, lignes directrices ou caract\u00e9ristiques \u00e0 utiliser syst\u00e9matiquement pour assurer l\u2019aptitude \u00e0 l\u2019emploi des mat\u00e9riaux, produits, processus et services.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><div class=\"push \" style=\"height:10px\"><\/div><\/div>\n\t<\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"wpv-grid grid-1-2  unextended no-extended-padding\" style=\"padding-top:0.05px;padding-bottom:0.05px;\" id=\"wpv-column-790b46a46cf7320fffb54a60fd1b73ce\" >\n<div  data-target=\"_self\" class=\"linkarea clearfix accent5  background-transparent\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"last\"><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>TYPOLOGIES DES NORMES<\/strong><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Les normes fondamentales<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Elles portent sur la terminologie, la m\u00e9trologie, les conventions, les signes, les symboles\u2026<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Les normes de sp\u00e9cifications<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Elles fixent les caract\u00e9ristiques d\u2019un produit ou d\u2019un service et leurs seuils de performances \u00e0 atteindre (aptitude \u00e0 l\u2019emploi, interface et interchangeabilit\u00e9, sant\u00e9, s\u00e9curit\u00e9, protection de l\u2019environnement, contrats-types, documentation accompagnant le produit ou le service\u2026).<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Les normes de m\u00e9thodes d\u2019essai et d\u2019analyse<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Ces normes mesurent les caract\u00e9ristiques et les performances d\u2019un produit.<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Les normes d\u2019organisation et de services<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Elles portent d\u2019une part sur la description et la mod\u00e9lisation des fonctions de l\u2019entreprise (maintenance, \u00a0logistique, management de la qualit\u00e9, gestion de production\u2026) et d\u2019autre part sur la d\u00e9finition et les performances des activit\u00e9s de services.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><div class=\"push \" style=\"height:10px\"><\/div><\/div>\n\t<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":11851,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_mi_skip_tracking":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_active":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_note":"","_monsterinsights_sitenote_category":0,"footnotes":""},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/11864"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=11864"}],"version-history":[{"count":44,"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/11864\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":14011,"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/11864\/revisions\/14011"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/11851"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=11864"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}